            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, heat a large-wide based pan (preferably non-stick) with a small drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>pork mince</strong> (remove the paper if required!) and cook for 6-7 min or until nicely browned, breaking it up with a wooden spoon as you go</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-copy-3-1681912412857-x200.jpg",
