            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the pork is browning, combine your<strong> hoisin sauce </strong>with 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[150ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[175ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Add your<strong> soy sauce</strong>, <strong>chilli flakes </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and a pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and stir it all together – this is your <strong>hoisin stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
