            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the pork is browned, add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong> to the pan with the <strong>chopped lemongrass</strong>, <strong>chopped ginger</strong> and<strong> chopped coriander stems</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and cook for 30 secs or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>hoisin stock</strong>, mix it all together and cook for 3-4 min or until it's reduced to a bolognese-like consistency and the pork is cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>fragrant pork</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
