    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top the <strong>roast aubergine </strong>with the <strong>fragrant pork</strong> – this is your <strong>Cambodian-style aubergine</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>Cambodian-style aubergine</strong> with the <strong>lemongrass rice</strong> to the side</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>reserved coriander leaves</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
